max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" class=\"wp-image-607624 alignnone size-landscape_thumbnail\" alt=\"Road tech newsletter\" title=\"Road tech newsletter\" />                                            <body><p>Here at BikeRadar, we’re obsessed with road cycling tech. Working closely with <a href=\"https://www.cyclingplus.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cycling Plus</a>, we report on <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">road bike tech news and new bike launches</a>, and also provide <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/reviews/bikes/road-bikes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">expert reviews</a> and impartial buying advice.</p>\n<p>Whether you’ve come to BikeRadar to ogle the latest and greatest road cycling tech or you want to <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/pro-bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">take a close look at what the pros ride</a>, we’ve got something for you.</p>\n<p>Our new fortnightly newsletter will bring you the finest selection of road cycling tech from across BikeRadar.</p>\n<p>Just sign-up below to start receiving the newsletter today.</p>\n<p>If you prefer off-road riding, why not check out our <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/gravel-tech-newsletter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">gravel</a> or <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/mountain-bike-tech-newsletter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mountain bike</a> newsletters? If you love sniffing out a bargain, <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/bikeradar-deals-newsletter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">BikeRadar Bargains</a> is the one for you.</p>\n\n<p> </p></body>","author":"Jack Luke","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"e0b83c94196e3a0f9d5b9355588243567960b15556a0804223093e3789b2c4e6","category":"Cycling"}